com.gwidgets.api.leaflet

Class L

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwidgets.api.leaflet.L

  • @JsType(isNative=true,
        namespace="<global>")
public class L
extends java.lang.Object
    The Master class of leaflet. All leaflet classes should be created through this class. This class transcribes factory methods from the Javascript version. It powers the OOP facilities of Leaflet.
    Author:
    Zakaria Amine
